g":"今朝坐巴士有個肥婆坐格離 勁大陣汗味 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b2be93b7ac732627b21957ec0195e0b8429800","tid":773822,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:34:08.000Z","msg":"好多時唔夠位晒衫都會好臭 又係土地問題<br />\n<br />\n或者晒衫時長開抽濕機"},{"pid":"612545eb2739c2a10a9bdcb611a8521d6aaca2b5","tid":773822,"uid":60916,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"老實講同沖涼 平時生活飲食習慣有關<br />\n以前細個成日唔做運動同食好多油膩野嗰身會好臭<br />\n大個左生活運動飲食模式轉左 d汗都冇咁臭<br />\n<br />\n係d廢中老又食煙又盛 朝早出門前又唔執先咁姐<br />\n<br />\n我平時巴士都好驚同廢中老坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404059017f7626e8aaa96a40460be21f38e30b25","tid":773822,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/7IW5YxuCPiy1zg9mTg/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F7IW5YxuCPiy1zg9mTg%2Fgiphy.gif&h=54a0b29a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3281fe205c3e568df549473a45da534000bafad0","tid":773822,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"真係好難頂 有啲一睇就知係啱啱出門都有一陣臭味"},{"pid":"81629a084036a474f2a19946983bcc5393fe42ab","tid":773822,"uid":108501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bfb3df28dba504554c053aae53cc848d42db81","tid":773822,"uid":116330,"like":371,"dislike":10,"score":361,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"其實咁臭佢地自己聞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"其實聞到 咁你想點"},{"pid":"6f844ea556405c4535cfc2a0198df184eada5008","tid":773822,"uid":63039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:33:01.000Z","msg":"1）<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/163157_bc9218a337d8846